  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3645741/" class="title-link">不一样的时代感的另类论语</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3645741"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/32392633/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/32392633/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">雪山飞狐</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-09-05"
      class="main-meta">2010-09-05 18:56:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3645741_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本论语有着强烈的文化大革命的时代气息，读起来确实别有一番风味，书中除了有些受到当时批孔批儒的政冶因素影响的内容不敢苟同外，其他的内容从另一角度理解论语这是当今其他版本的所不具有的。值的论语爱好者好好读一回！

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
